						"Details": "As [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreKuritaDCMS],DCMS]] units focused on repelling the Dominion forces, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSandoval],Duke Sandoval]] of Robinson instigated an invasion of the Combine of his own with Draconis March armed forces. With the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFedCom],Federated Commonwealth]] in the midst of its own civil war, it is unclear whether the March's invasion represents a bid for independence for the March worlds or an offering to either Steiner or Davion. In a near mirror image, reports from the Clan Occupation Zones indicate that [[DM.Factions[faction_ClanHellsHorses],Clan Hell's Horses]] may be mobilizing against their old rivals in the Dominion.",
